title: Doctor Who - First and Last Stories of the 8th Doctor
description:
The Canadian Doctor, as I like to call him, because this Doctor Who reboot was shot as a backdoor pilot in Vancouver, B.C.

Not exactly a brilliant story, but it did show a brilliant steampunk and huge TARDIS set.

I've added the Night of the Doctor minisode as a bookend to the televised adventures of the Eighth Doctor.

The movie was transcoded by Handbrake from the original DVD source, while Night of the Doctor was downloaded and reupped.
